file.name: no-content.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Swagger Petstore
  license:
    name: MIT
servers:
  - url: http://petstore.swagger.io/v1
paths:
  /pets/{pet_id}:
    parameters:
      - name: pet_id
        in: path
        required: true
        schema:
          type: integer
    delete:
      operationId: deletePet
      responses:
        '204':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
    get:
      operationId: showPet
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
        '423':
          description: 'Locked'
